articles.author: Francisco Guzman
articles.title: 3 US Marines killed, 20 injured after aircraft crash in Australia during training exercise - USA TODAY
articles.description: Three U.S. Marines are dead and 20 others were injured after a Marine Corps aircraft crashed in Australia during a training exercise.
articles.content:
Three U.S. Marines died and 20 others were injured after a Marine Corps aircraft crashed in Australia during a training exercise Sunday, officials said.
